high_descs: Turn to the right and go across the room. Turn to the right again, and then the left at the counter beside the stove.
Pick up the spatula from the counter.
Take the spatula and turn around to the sink.
Place the spatula in the sink, turn on the water and then off again. Pick up the spatula.
Take the spatula and turn around to the counter.
Open the top drawer and place the spatula inside.
anns.task_desc: Clean a spatula to put it away.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the fridge.  Turn right and walk to the counter that is to the right of the fridge. Face the counter.
Pick up the spatula that is on the counter in front of the bread.
Holding the spatula, turn around 180 degrees to face the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink to the left of the tomato, fill the sink with water, then drain the sink. Take the spatula from out of the sink.
Turn around 180 degrees to face the stove top and counter to the left of the stove top.
Open the top drawer that is left of the stove top underneath the counter, place the spatula in the drawer, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed spatula into a drawer.

high_descs: turn to the right and move across the room towards the refrigerator, turn right at the refrigerator moving forward towards the dishwasher on the left, turn left to face the counter
pick up the spatula that is on the counter in front of the loaf of bread on the right
turn around and move towards the sink
put the spatula into the sink and turn on the water to clean the spatula and pick up the spatula out from of the sink
turn around to face the counter to the left of the stove
open the top drawer that is to the left of the stove, put the spatula into the drawer and close it
anns.task_desc: put a clean spatula into the drawer
